Erin Fitzgerald https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Erin_Fitzgerald 0 Erin Fitzgerald is a Canadian-American voice actress who provides voice-overs for a number of cartoons, video games and English language dubs of Japanese anime. In animation, she voices May Kanker and Nazz in Ed, Edd n Eddy, and voices major characters in The Jungle Bunch, Batman: Year One, Monster High and Ever After High. In video games, she voices female leads Yrel in World of Warcraft: Warlords of Draenor, Chie Satonaka in the Persona 4 series of games starting with Persona 4 Golden and Noire in the Hyperdimension Neptunia series. In anime shows, she has voiced in Sailor Moon, Bleach, Naruto Shippuden, Knights of Sidonia and Glitter Force.
